being a little selfish?

95
00:07:23,777 --> 00:07:26,079
What?

96
00:07:26,113 --> 00:07:30,183
I'm talking to you
about spending the rest
of our lives together here

97
00:07:30,217 --> 00:07:33,086
in this town,
about raising kids,

98
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:36,557
here in this town.

99
