what it takes to make it.

104
00:07:52,472 --> 00:07:55,042
Yeah, I'm real sorry, okay?

105
00:07:55,075 --> 00:07:59,079
But somebody had to tell
you the truth. It's for
your own good, Maggie.

106
00:08:02,249 --> 00:08:04,051
To hell with you.

107
00:08:04,084 --> 00:08:07,721
Just trying to spare
you some grief, Maggie.

108
00:08:14,528 --> 00:08:15,696
Daddy.

109
00:08:18,298 --> 00:08:20,634
