00:38:26,938 --> 00:38:28,273
and they listen
to some music.

525
00:38:28,306 --> 00:38:31,009
- What a great idea.
- Yeah.

526
00:38:31,042 --> 00:38:34,913
A lot of the classics
have been remastered,

527
00:38:34,946 --> 00:38:37,416
but we got pretty much
a lot of everything.

528
00:38:37,449 --> 00:38:40,118
So what do you like?

529
00:38:40,151 --> 00:38:43,622
I don't know if I'd
know most of these,
I'm embarrassed to admit.

