00:38:43,655 --> 00:38:45,891
Yeah, so, what?
You're not really
a music lover?

531
00:38:45,924 --> 00:38:48,360
I am. I am.
Music is my life.

532
00:38:48,394 --> 00:38:51,497
I love to sing.
I'm inspired by
Aretha Franklin,

533
00:38:51,530 --> 00:38:54,299
but I don't have much
knowledge of anyone
besides her.

534
00:38:54,332 --> 00:38:56,702
Are you serious
about your singing?

535
00:38:56,735 --> 00:38:58,637
Yes, I am.

536
00:38:58,670 --> 00:39:03,409
So how about Thelma Jones,

537
00:39:03,442 --> 00:39:04,910
Barbara McNair,

538
00:39:04,943 --> 00:39:07,078
Big Mama Thornton?

539
00:39:10,382 --> 00:39:13,151
