00:39:58,564 --> 00:40:00,832
Nothing. He's a nice guy.

555
00:40:00,866 --> 00:40:03,001
That's it, isn't it?
He's too nice.

556
00:40:03,034 --> 00:40:04,870
What's that supposed
to mean?

557
00:40:04,903 --> 00:40:07,639
That's why you don't like him.
He's a nice guy.
I know your type.

558
00:40:07,673 --> 00:40:10,208
You are making all this up.
You realize that?

559
00:40:10,241 --> 00:40:12,511
So are you gonna explain
the clothes and the get-up?

560
00:40:12,544 --> 00:40:16,648
- 'Cause you look nice.
- That's the idea.
 I got a date.

561
00:40:16,682 --> 00:40:21,587
All right, the plan is
I look absolutely smashing.

562
00:40:21,620 --> 00:40:24,122
I get him all excited,

563
00:40:24,155 --> 00:40:25,924
treat him like shit
the entire night.

564
00:40:25,957 --> 00:40:29,495
Whoo! Healthy relationship.
Good for you.

565
00:40:29,528 --> 00:40:31,362
I gotta go.
I don't wanna keep
him waiting.

566
00:40:31,396 --> 00:40:35,200
- Oh, heaven forbid. Bye.
- Bye.

567
00:40:42,941 --> 00:40:46,344
* He's so crazy

568
00:40:47,378 --> 00:40:50,081
* Yeah, he's crazy

569
