[Maggie] Oh.

704
00:49:41,079 --> 00:49:42,947
Hi.

705
00:49:45,083 --> 00:49:48,553
This is my roommate
Rachel-- Mr. Rachel. Sorry.

706
00:49:48,586 --> 00:49:51,722
This is my friend
Julia and Cory.

707
00:49:51,756 --> 00:49:53,424
How do you do?

708
00:49:53,458 --> 00:49:56,161
Hi. Nice to meet you.

709
00:49:56,194 --> 00:49:58,196
Wow.

710
00:49:58,229 --> 00:50:02,733
[laughs] This is
a regular arcade. Awesome.

711
00:50:02,767 --> 00:50:06,471
You two play
with these things?

712
00:50:06,504 --> 00:50:09,074
Not in this heat we don't.

713
00:50:09,107 --> 00:50:12,009
Damn hot, isn't it?

714
00:50:12,043 --> 00:50:14,812
I'll tell you,
all you want to do
is sleep during the day.

715
00:50:14,845 --> 00:50:18,583
But when you lay down,
you can't fall asleep
'cause it's too damn hot.

716
00:50:18,616 --> 00:50:21,052
You're damn right
it's too damn hot.

717
00:50:21,086 --> 00:50:23,254
I know.
I agree it's miserable.

718
00:50:23,288 --> 00:50:25,090
It's absolutely miserable.

719
00:50:27,158 --> 00:50:30,395
You know, they do have
these new things now.
These new inventions.

720
00:50:30,428 --> 00:50:33,598
Maybe you heard of them.
They're air conditioners.

721
00:50:33,631 --> 00:50:35,233
Boo.

722
00:50:35,266 --> 00:50:37,568
They make too much racket.

723
00:50:37,602 --> 00:50:40,471
See, smart-ass,
too much racket.

724
00:50:40,505 --> 00:50:42,240
Agreed again.

725
00:50:45,810 --> 00:50:49,280
[Maggie]
Okay, well, let's go.

726
00:50:49,314 --> 00:50:52,750
Let's go. Come on.

727
00:50:54,619 --> 00:50:56,887
- Nice to meet you.
- Yeah.

728
00:50:56,921 --> 00:51:00,491
- [Rachel] Pleasure is all mine.
- Yeah. Good night.

729
00:51:00,525 --> 00:51:02,627
[mouths]

730
00:51:05,163 --> 00:51:07,098
See you later.

731
00:51:08,333 --> 00:51:10,067
[scoffs]

732
00:51:15,640 --> 00:51:19,244
Yeah, that's right.

733
00:51:19,277 --> 00:51:22,480
Leave me alone in this...

734
00:51:22,513 --> 00:51:25,450
in this heat.

735
00:51:25,483 --> 00:51:27,518
[laughing]

736
00:51:27,552 --> 00:51:29,620
