00:52:38,523 --> 00:52:40,725
Hello.
All right, listen up.

746
00:52:40,758 --> 00:52:43,261
We have with us
a special guest.

747
00:52:43,294 --> 00:52:45,129
She's only in town
for one night.

748
00:52:45,162 --> 00:52:46,831
She's only got time
for one song

749
00:52:46,864 --> 00:52:48,399
'cause she's gotta catch
a plane to go to London.

750
00:52:48,433 --> 00:52:50,401
You've heard about her
for years, so come on, man,

751
00:52:50,435 --> 00:52:54,339
put it together
for Rod Stewart's "Maggie May!"

