00:53:01,612 --> 00:53:03,781
[sound effects over dialogue]

755
00:53:32,243 --> 00:53:34,612
[heart beating]

756
00:53:34,645 --> 00:53:37,248
[panting]

757
00:53:46,557 --> 00:53:48,859
